data.description: 4-bedroom 2 bath home conveniently located to everything! Walking distance to elementary school, minutes to shopping, restaurants and interstate. Spacious living area with laminate wood flooring, gas burning fireplace. Open to the dining and kitchen area for all your entertaining. Kitchen has double pantry and freshly painted cabinets. Primary bedroom has trey ceilings, bath with double vanities, soaking tub and separate shower. Garage is temporarily a bonus room, can be converted back. Covered back patio. Call today and schedule your showing!
